 -> Retention : How long kafka stores messages
 -> Replication : Kafka keep copies of messages for safety
 -> producer Acknowledgement : Ways to confirm if message was successfully sent
 -> Dead Letter Queue(DLQ) : Special place to store failed messages
 -> Kafka Connect : Tool to connect kafka with databases, cloud etc
 -> Kafka Stream : Allows you to process data inside Kafka in real-time
 
   	
   	
